            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "`vim.treesitter.stop` in `b:undo_ftplugin` invokes `TSHighlighter:destroy`, which executes `syntaxset` `FileType` autocommands.\n\nThat causes the modeline to be processed again, which sets `&filetype` back to `help`, `b:undo_ftplugin` tries to clear the mappings again but fails, and `&filetype` remains as `help` from the 2nd processing of the modeline.\n\nMaybe `modeline = false` should be added to `nvim_exec_autocmds` in `TSHighlighter:destroy` instead.",
